"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The means of salvation for Israel in the wilderness, a parallel to be found in Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Healing and salvation resulted from looking at the bronze snake</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:8-Num21:9\">NUM 21:8–21:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:4-Num21:7\">NUM 21:4–21:7</a></p>\n<h2>The bronze snake became an object of idolatrous worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:4\">2KI 18:4</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The bronze snake parallels Jesus Christ's crucifixion</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14-John3:15\">JHN 3:14–3:15</a></strong></p>",
